list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: New Accounts will now automatically join the 2009Scape clan chat Renamed the Server's account to '2009Scape' within the members table of the global.sql database The automatic clan chat join can be toggled on or off on the Management Server's ServerConstants.java file Added some text in the TutorialCompletionDialogue.java file to simulate joining the clan once the player has reached the mainland. Added some comments to properly denote what is happening. Added spawns for Melee Dummy and Magic Dummy in the Lumbridge Combat Hall in the server.sql database.
